I".<p>记录使用vue-fullpage.js遇到的问题。</p>

<p>github地址：https://github.com/alvarotrigo/vue-fullpage.js</p>

<p>下载安装
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">npm install --save vue-fullpage.js</code></p>

<p>index.html页面</p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="cp">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;html&gt;</span>
